Description :
        It's None Other Than Him, Fei Qi Mo Shu, Fi Q M Sh,  at manhua websiteWhen he woke up, things had changed, and Neil discovered that his last memory was from ten thousand years ago. Later, he discovered that the space he was in was not his original world. The chaotic flow of time and space appeared in different dimensions, and more and more things gradually appeared. Friends who had similar experiences to him decided to use the power of the clock tower guardians and doors to connect to the outside world and collect more clues. Many unexpected stories happened in the process.Recommend for you !
